@startuml
title AudioFileHeader_accessory
hide footbox

skinparam  defaultFontName Courier
skinparam shadowing false

participant AudioFileHeader as afh
participant AudioFileHeader_accessory as afha
participant AudioFileHeader_accessory_Presenter as afhap

autonumber
afh ->> afha : audio id
afha ->> afhap : audio id
afhap ->> afhap : edit sample and delete sample\ndialogs as render functions
opt if route is "Quick Save"
    afhap ->> afhap : assign sample dialog as render functions
end
afhap ->> afha : list of render functions
afha ->> afha : render drop-down menu \nand dialog render functions\n in render()


